snippet: Gov. Scott Walker’s national profile clearly has already risen, but he says he is only focused on Wisconsin for now.
abstract: Gov Scott Walker's national profile has risen due to his victory in the bitterly fought recall election in Wisconsin; Walker insists that he remains focused on his own state, but he is already being considered as a potential candidate for higher office by members of the Republican elite.

byline.contributor: Steven Yaccino contributed reporting from Milwaukee.

lead_paragraph: Gov. Scott Walker’s national profile clearly has already risen, but he says he is only focused on Wisconsin for now.

headline.seo: Talk of Higher Office Swirls Around Wisconsin’s Scott Walker
headline.main: Talk of Higher Office Swirls Around Wisconsin Governor in the Spotlight
headline.print_headline: Talk of Higher Office Swirls Around Wisconsin Governor in the Spotlight
